game.name: Mommy Photo Album
game.description:
Pregnancy is a very special time for every woman. This mommy is also no different so she has also decided to do something different to cherish her pregnancy time. She has already visited a popular and professional photo studio to take her picture. All is good, but this cute pregnant woman does not know what to put on to look awesome on her first photoshoot. Dress her up and then help the lady to frame her photo in Mommy Photo Album!

Find a wide array of trendy and cool outfits for a new mommy and help her to grab a wonderful photo album from the magical time of her life in this cute HTML5 dressing game! Try to make this pregnant photo session memorable forever! Style her hair with two futuristic buns or glitter and then combine it with a strapless red outfit with a purple bow! You can also opt for a teal pleated skirt or a pink top and pair it with a colorful necklace.

She will also look awesome with an off-shoulder blue top and a pair of matching paints that come with some purple glittery lines. A pair of comfy shoes will help lady to get a complete look. You also have a full freedom to change the background and help girl to know whether she has a boy or a girl. Decorate her background with a painting of a magical night in Paris or some adorable animals in this decoration mobile game! Feel free to add some toys, a crib or some cute balloons to make it look fabulous!
